snippet.textDisplay:
Let me share an anecdote from my life. I played a few Bangla songs while i was sitting with my friends and colleagues from around the world. They were mesmerized by the song and music although they didnt understand the language.
If this song was available then I would have proudly played it to present our diversity in Bangladesh and South Asia. 
Salute and hats off to the people who sang in this song. Would look forward to more from them all.
